{{DISPLAYTITLE:FMP_DIRECTION}}
{{TAGDEF|FMP_DIRECTION|1 {{!}} 2 {{!}} 3 | 3}}

Description: Index of the lattice vector <math>\mathbf{a}_i</math> along which the temperature gradient is created in the ([[Müller-Plathe method]]).

-----

{{TAG|FMP_DIRECTION}} defines the index of the lattice vector <math>\mathbf{a}_i</math> along which the gradient <math>\partial T/\partial \mathbf{a}_i </math> is created during the reverse nonequilibrium molecular-dynamics run using the [[Müller-Plathe method]].
{{NB|mind|This tag will only be available from VASP 6.4.4}}
